- The initial version of our Phoenix reporting engine is completed
and in QA for review.
- Development of the P2PE integration to the new VX820 device
was completed and passed QA testing.
		- We anticipate certification to be completed by the end of the
month.
- Work has begun on the planning and layout of the new data
center to support Phoenix’s needs.
- We will be deploying EMV on the VX805/820 this week.

As always, let me know if you need anything.

Thanks
